## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **dupilumab COPD 2024** = first FDA biologic for COPD. T2-high eosinophilic subset 만 (≥300 eos/µL). selectivity 향상 path 가 quantum-VQE 의 의의.
2. **sotatercept PAH 2024** = first activin-class PAH (Winrevair). BMP/activin imbalance 정상화 → 우심부전 mortality 향상. quantum-VQE 의 ActRIIA + sotatercept-Fc fusion extracellular interface 가 hxq-pulm-actr2a-001 candidate motivation.
3. **ensifentrine COPD 2024** = first new COPD class in 20+ yrs (PDE3 + PDE4 dual). quantum-VQE 의 dual-pocket selectivity 가 의미 있는 in-silico distinguishing feature.
4. **Trikafta 2019 CF F508del 90% coverage** — corrector + potentiator combo 의 quantum-VQE structural-biology 도 historical 가치. 나머지 10% (rare CFTR) 가 next quantum target.
5. **MASH dupilumab + COPD dupilumab + AD dupilumab + EoE dupilumab** = IL-4Rα 의 pan-T2 hub. quantum-VQE 의 IL-4Rα Fab 가 multi-disease leverage candidate.
6. **CF gene therapy AAV airway = historical fail-mode** (1990s-2000s, immunogenicity + epithelium turnover). lentivirus / mRNA-LNP 가 next-gen — VIROCAPSID + WEAVE 의 cross-axis 가 의미.
7. **AATD systemic IV augmentation = 1987 standard** — fazirsiran (siRNA SERPINA1 Z-mutant) 가 2024 Phase 3 land. RIBOZYME axis 의 즉시-적용 path.
8. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, pulmonology 임상 의미 한정.

